### List all programs
GET {{baseUrl}}/programs
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
 
### Get a single program with funding status
GET {{baseUrl}}/programs/seed-program-001
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
 
### Create a program (Admin only)
POST {{baseUrl}}/programs
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json
 
{
  "name": "Emergency Relief Fund Q1",
  "type": "emergency",
  "budgetTarget": 50000,
  "region": "East Africa",
  "description": "Emergency food relief for drought-affected areas"
}
 
### Get program funding progress
GET {{baseUrl}}/programs/seed-program-001/funding-status
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

